Figure 6a shows experimental and simulated the reflectance spectra of the prepared NP-GaN DBR. According to the volume averaging theory22, the effective refractive index of the NP-GaN layer can be calculated by using the follow equation:n=(1-φ)nGaN2+φnair2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
